---
title: HelloHero: Spiced Halloumi & Jewell Couscous with Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Couscous - the grain so nice they named it twice! Here we’ve added sweet currants and crunchy almonds for a pop of flavour, and topped the whole thing off with mildly spiced halloumi and greens. Don’t forget a generous dollop of cooling yoghurt to
bring the meal together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66fe06e4966ea033d562d55a-20ef6c7b.jpeg
